{"tid":1753298,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"外國觀察團憂港操控選舉","createTime":"2019-11-25T02:18:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T02:40:03.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"157c41d52f80a91cea7d2892f618e06211ad37ed","tid":1753298,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T02:18:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191125/LOECUPBIWG6AYEVT4ZIMLMRNSY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191125%2FLOECUPBIWG6AYEVT4ZIMLMRNSY%2F&d=dTdn096UhK%2BcydR5vLM293JTAtm2oKGHsrawk8oVPbs%3D&h=da92a0b5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191125%2FLOECUPBIWG6AYEVT4ZIMLMRNSY%2F&h=743ceb25\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191125/LOECUPBIWG6AYEVT4ZIMLMRNSY/</a><br />\n<br />\n外國觀察團憂港操控選舉<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191125/large/1574614675_193d.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191125%2Flarge%2F1574614675_193d.gif&h=c1ef0630&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n多國專家組成的「獨立選舉監察小組」，昨午到各票站監察區會選舉。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【黃 埔】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】獲「我要攬炒」團隊邀請來港，來自英國、丹麥、瑞典、日本等多國專家組成的「獨立選舉監察小組」，昨午兵分三路到九龍、新界、港島的票站監察區議會選舉。成員擔心政府會想辦法操縱選舉。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對高投票率感鼓舞<br />\n<br />\n英國保守黨人權委員會委員Luke de Pulford是九龍小隊的成員之一。Luke表示，自己早上已親自到過5、6個票站視察，他認為整體運作暢順，但他親眼見過有票站讓老人家率先投票，跳過長長人龍。他指，英國的選舉不會有這樣的安排，若選舉的投票率很高，可能會令年輕人排很長時間才能投票，令人感到不公，但難言是否錯誤。他最初擔心市民會因為覺得選舉的作用有限而不出來投票，但現時的高投票率令他感鼓舞。<br />\n<br />\n前立陶宛議員Mantas Adom&eacute;nas及瑞典政黨成員Olle Johnsson等人就來到太古西東區少年警訊會所票站，與民主派候選人趙家賢會面。Olle Johnsson認為，雖然高投票率令外界預測民主派能大勝，但他並不樂觀，仍擔心中央政府會操縱選舉。<br />\n<br />\n區選首次獲極大國際關注，趙家賢認為，今次抗爭運動凸顯了政府管治失效，制度運作失能，因此「更加需要外國社會朋友嚟，咁樣先至能有效監察呢個專制政府會唔會做手腳」。監察小組的每個小隊會視察最少十個票站，但由於票站主任不允許監察員入內，所以未能見證實際投票情況。<br />\n<br />\n■記者關冠麒、鄭祉愉"},{"pid":"4f0301e7bcdce58e80e1adbdd9fd9ed77e800d5c","tid":1753298,"uid":45983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T02:22:34.000Z","msg":"佢有無睇最後監票"},{"pid":"b5c050fd1853c64f2fd90ae780849e021b773bdb","tid":1753298,"uid":27319,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T02:26:50.000Z","msg":"泛民大勝 證明選舉係公平公正公開 無被人操控<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8ff8ef0b81ebe737bdf845b2c0d637a3d718297","tid":1753298,"uid":392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T02:28:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b2eca15d28ddd8f4cf74e2d52e180308fd041fe","tid":1753298,"uid":258649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b5c050fd1853c64f2fd90ae780849e021b773bdb","tid":1753298,"uid":27319,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T02:26:50.000Z","msg":"泛民大勝 證明選舉係公平公正公開 無被人操控<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T02:28:20.000Z","msg":"險勝咋，扣番廢老種票個d先係大勝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"331dd9b1ccbccdd56c7c1a5ddb968462f9bc3e99","tid":1753298,"uid":10125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T02:31:41.000Z","msg":"對家操控完都輸咋"},{"pid":"d914765c4b04cd317a149547a5021540ef7f6d07","tid":1753298,"uid":119271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T02:40:03.000Z","msg":"贏左都要關注返選舉舞弊"}]}